net.sf.jclec.mo.comparator.fcomparator

Class MOValueFitnessComparator

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.jclec.mo.comparator.fcomparator.MOFitnessComparator
      • net.sf.jclec.mo.comparator.fcomparator.MOValueFitnessComparator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Comparator<net.sf.jclec.IFitness>

    public class MOValueFitnessComparator
extends MOFitnessComparator
    Compare two MOFitness objects based on the fitness value. By default, this comparator considers a maximization problem, i.e. greater fitness values are preferred, although minimization problems can be also considered setting the inversion flag.

    HISTORY:

    • (AR|JRR|SV, 1.0, March 2018) First release.

    1.0
